confixx License Checker Plugin
------------------------------

This plugin connects to the confixx-mysql Database
and checks if the attribute for the license show
a correct set up license.

Installation

Set up a user, which has select permissions
on the confixx table "register". Confixx-DB
Name "confixx" assumed.

mysql -uroot -p.... -Dconfixx
> grant select on confixx.register to 'licence_manager'@'localhost' identified by 'your-password-here';
> flush privileges;

